“This bench has been repossessed by the
people, owing to the bankers of the
City of London faliling to meet thelr obligtions
to repay the taxpaying public for bailing them
out of the mess they caused.
If you are a banker, please sit elsewhere."°
§To remember with great love
Diana Constance Simmonds
(1929-2017) (Mum, Gran, Di-Di)
The most wonderful and loyal mother, grandmother, friend and neighbour
She lived in Holborn for most of her life and loved this square. "I know we'll meet again""■
